title: No ranked end-of-season rewards yet
body: Is this normal or should I open a ticket regarding the subject?

replies.body: This is normal, there are a lot of players in each region that we need to distribute rewards to.  We're going to need some time!  Keep an eye on our [helpdesk ](https://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/player-support/W0aEONuP-2017-ranked-rewards-help-desk)thread for updates.
Just keep waiting, it will come eventualy.
